reviewText: I bought this for my daughter's kindergarten class valentine's day party. She said they loved it!
Bought this for the grandchildren. They really enjoyed it. Has plenty of action and  good family values. I would recommend this for all ages.
I didn't even watch this- crazy day- but it kept my two younger kids busy this afternoon so I could get some stuff done and that, in my book, deserves a five star rating. :-)
